snippet.title: Colossal Dwarfare DLC Trailer |  Kingdom Rush 5: Alliance
snippet.description:
🤖 A Dwarven madman is threatening the Kingdom with a colossal war automaton. The Alliance must race to the Darksteel Mountains to stop its construction before it’s too late!
⚙️ Colossal Dwarfare – New DLC coming to Kingdom Rush Alliance on January 30th! Wishlist now on Steam: https://bit.ly/Colossal-Dwarfare-Steam

⚙️ Colossal Dwarfare contents: ⚙️
- 5 New Stages: race through the Darksteel Mountains!
- 12 Deadly Enemies: Face sinister clones and mechanical monstrosities!
- 1 New Tower: Cannoneer Squad – explosive firepower for Linirea!
- 1 New Hero: Kratoa, the Molten Rage – fury from the Dark Army!
- 2 Minibosses & 3 Boss Fights waiting to be disassembled!
- New Achievements for ultimate bragging rights!

Join the Discord Server: https://discord.gg/ABkzxVTZ
